manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Introducing Trianium’s Tempered Glass Screen Protector for iPhone XS Max 2018 and iPhone 11 Pro Max 2019 (6.5" Screen) Due to the curved-edge design of the iPhone X Max & iPhone 11 Pro Max, our screen protector is made to be a little smaller than the actual screen of your device. This helps to prevent protector from overlaying these curved edge which can lead to unwanted bubbles or peeling up around the edges. Durable and scratch resistant screen protector offers your phone protection against scratches, bumps, drops, and daily wear and tear. Easy to install screen protector allows for complete touchscreen sensitive, you won’t even know it’s there! Clean the phone screen thoroughly using the wet & dry wipes before installation. Peel off the protective layer (with tab) from the screen protector before applying to the phone. If air bubbles are present, use squeegee or hard card to push bubble from the center away to the edge of the phone screen. The curved-edge design is made smaller than the screen size of your device to ensure unwanted peeling or bubbling appear around edges.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 10, 2019
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Quality Screen Protector from Trianium
reviews.reviewText: Trianium delivers a functional and practical screen protector for the iPhone XS Max. I've had the pleasure of owning several Trianium brand screen protectors, and not one screen has cracked from a fall. In everyday usage, these protectors are great at saving your screen from a replacement. In my experience it has taken several forceful falls before needing a replacement. One screen protector lasts me between 3-4 months. I appreciate the typical Trianium packaging--these screen protectors come in cases of three. More protectors per order means fewer times I need to reorder. For their price, these screen protectors are a great lesser-known brand that will protect your phone without paying leading brand prices. There are clear and simple instructions on how to install these, leaving few to no air bubbles on your phone. Although I'm sure my phone is already adequately protected, a slightly thicker glass may put my mind at greater ease. I recommend checking these screen protectors out if you need a durable screen protector for everyday use (minor falls and slip-ups) without overspending on a glass protector.
